title: SPENCER, LAB BLUE AND WHITE SAPPHIRE STUDS
description:
Oversized studs that are easy to wear yet impactful. A halo of lab-grown white sapphires surround a 2 carat oval cut blue sapphire on our Spencer Studs.  
Spencer is part of a limited winter collection run. This style will not return in 2023 once sold out.
details:
Metal: Sterling silver
Stone Type: Lab-grown blue and white sapphire
Stone Shape: Oval and round cut  



4.00 CTW DEW lab-grown blue sapphire center
1.44 CTW DEW lab-grown white sapphire halo
